 auth/token lifecycle, mcp-refero transport-packet layout mapped on mcp-figma\",\"findingsCount\":4,\"newInfoRatio\":0.7,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Substantially new angles — gating/rate-limit gap confirmed as negative knowledge, first-use browser-sign-in constraint, full packet layout + Code Mode calling convention — none present in iteration 1; some consolidation of iteration-1 tool-surface facts.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"q2\",\"q3\",\"q4\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"q2\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Further scraping of refero.design/* SPA routes for pricing/gating\",\"reason\":\"All routes yield only the title; pricing/gating facts are not web-crawlable\",\"evidence\":\"lineages/glm/iterations/iteration-002.md F7\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-16T12:50:00Z\",\"durationMs\":90000}\n{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"dashboard_generated\",\"iteration\":2,\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-16T12:50:30Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-glm-1784198125985-iw9229\",\"generation\":1}\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/mcp-tooling/009-mcp-refero/001-research/research/lineages/glm/deep-research-state.jsonl"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/mcp-tooling/009-mcp-refero/001-research/research/lineages/glm/deep-research-state.jsonl","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/mcp-tooling/009-mcp-refero/001-research/research/lineages/glm/deep-research-state.jsonl","time":{"start":1784198979634,"end":1784198979638}},"id":"prt_f6a8be030001aWJpdDkPoWhnUp","sessionID":"ses_095812142ffehVMtk1LE9C34ba","messageID":"msg_f6a8b7d19001xLBbXSJCeuf6Oa"}}
