vey of Refero MCP surface (refero.design/mcp + refero_skill repo + .utcp manual)","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"content":"iteration 2: broaden angles (free/paid gating, auth/rate-limits depth, transport-packet conventions vs mcp-figma)","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"content":"phase_synthesis: compile research.md + convergence report + final JSONL","status":"in_progress","priority":"high"},{"content":"emit FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:glm","status":"pending","priority":"high"}],"truncated":false},"title":"2 todos","time":{"start":1784199102180,"end":1784199102181}},"id":"prt_f6a8dbedd001VHNI068eFyYdCV","sessionID":"ses_095812142ffehVMtk1LE9C34ba","messageID":"msg_f6a8d75890012WzpN0Yf01nsQP"}}
